  "description": "Erection of a part one-, part two- storey extension over lower ground and upper ground floors and erection of rear roof dormer extension to facilitate conversion of dwellinghouse to create 4x self-contained residential units with associated bike and bin storage",
  "lapsed_date": "22/02/2022",
  "lpa_app_no": "2021/2537",
  "last_updated": "2025-03-20T12:50:30.342+00:00",
  "application_type": "All Other",
  "site_name": null,
  "appeal_decision_date": null,
  "site_number": "58",
  "appeal_decision": null,
  "development_type": "Minor dwellings",
  "appeal_start_date": null,
  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-15fe4a38-7fff-2e00-9a7c-1a60b1c9670f&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The proposed development, by reason of inadequate unit sizes, bedrooms and head height, would result in a substandard level of accommodation for future occupiers contrary to policies D6 (Housing quality and standards) of The London Plan (2021), policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and LP17 (Housing Design) of the Hackney Local Plan (2020); and the guidance contained with the Hackney Residential Extensions and Alterations Supplementary Planning Document (2009) and the Housing SPG (2016).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;",
    "&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-0f3c759e-7fff-8740-29c9-8decd9db8429&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The proposed rear extension, by reason of its height, depth and resulting scale, would result in an loss of light and outlook and an overbearing development for the occupiers of 60 Kyverdale Road contrary to policy LP2 (Development and Amenity) of Hackney Local Plan 2033 (2020) and policy D6 (Housing quality and standards) of the London Plan (2021).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;",
    "&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-af7548f8-7fff-3dfb-4320-2b88bc1f099b&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The proposed conversion, by reason of failure to provide a four bedroom unit within the Stamford Hill AAP area would fail to adequately provide family accommodation in an area identified as in need of larger units, contrary to policies LP14 (Dwelling mix), and LP19 (Residential Conversions) of Hackney Local Plan 2033 (2020)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;",
    "In the absence of a contribution towards affordable housing either on site, or a financial payment in-lieu, the development fails to deliver the maximum reasonable amount of affordable housing and is therefore contrary to policy H4 (Delivering affordable housing) of the London Plan (2021), policy LP13 (Affordable housing) of Hackney’s Local Plan 2033 (2020) and Hackney&#39;s S106 Planning Contributions SPD (2020).",
    "The proposed development fails to provide adequate storage for bicycles contrary to policy LP42 of Hackney&#x27;s Local Plan 2033 (2020) and policy T5 of the London Plan (2021).&amp;nbsp;"
  ],
